sub_title: Senior Technical Advisor at Rutgers kenniscentrum seksualiteit
summary:
My professional interest lies at the intersection of development, Sexual and Reproductive Health, and Rights, and gender. I have strong expertise in conducting and teaching qualitative research. 
I have more than 15 years of experience in strategic design, implementation and evaluation of development projects in (international) development organizations. 
I seek to make important contributions to projects at the forefront of scientific research. I enjoy working in multicultural environments where I am continuously stimulated to develop my personal skills and knowledge.
